---
const WHOP_LINK = "https://whop.com/escapenazis";
---
<section class="vsl-section">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <h2 class="mb-4">Watch This Short Video Before You Proceed...</h2>
    <p class="mb-8" style="color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 3rem;">
      Discover exactly how energy vampires and negative entities attach themselves to you, and the simple framework we use to detach them permanently.
    </p>

    <div class="video-container glass-panel">
      <!-- VSL Placeholder Image with Play Button -->
      <!-- In production, drop a YouTube or Vimeo iframe here -->
      <div class="vsl-placeholder">
        <div class="play-button">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="vsl-text">Click to Play Video</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8">
      <a href={WHOP_LINK} class="btn-primary">
        Yes, I'm Ready To Protect Myself
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .vsl-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.3); /* Subtle backdrop */
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
  }

  .video-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1rem; /* Thin border/glass effect */
    border-radius: 20px;
  }

  .vsl-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    background: #000;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, #1e1b4b, #4c1d95, #000);
    background-size: 200% 200%;
    animation: gradientShift 10s ease infinite;
  }

  .play-button {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: var(--primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.6);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .play-button svg {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    color: white;
    margin-left: 5px;
  }

  .vsl-placeholder:hover .play-button {
    transform: scale(1.1);
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.9);
  }

  .vsl-text {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
  }

  @keyframes gradientShift {
    0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
    100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .vsl-section { padding: 4rem 0; }
    h2 { font-size: 2rem; }
    .play-button { width: 60px; height: 60px; }
    .play-button svg { width: 30px; height: 30px; }
    .vsl-text { font-size: 1rem; }
    .video-container { padding: 0.5rem; border-radius: 12px; }
    .vsl-placeholder { border-radius: 8px; }
  }
</style>
